## Intent

Explain the priorities of South African coffee buyers.

## Visible Text

### What South African Buyers Need

Consistent Quality

Reliable Supply

Origin Diversity

Blend Flexibility

Traceability

Commercial Reliability

### Why Uganda Can Compete

Uganda offers both Robusta and Arabica coffee, creating flexibility across commercial and premium segments.

Existing market participation demonstrates buyer acceptance.

## Image Brief

Professional buyer evaluation environment with coffee samples, cupping and sourcing decisions.
